Description: Bulk-migrate Proxmox VE guest storage between storages
 proxmox-storage-migrate bulk-migrates Proxmox VE guest storage (VM disks and
 container volumes) from one storage to another, optionally across an
 entire cluster, in parallel.
 .
 It wraps qm move-disk and pct move-volume with discovery, parallelism,
 QCOW2/raw format handling, TPM state and container shutdown handling,
 per-move verification, and logging.
 .
 Must be run as root on a Proxmox VE host (needs qm and/or pct).

